<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Setup - Memorial Website</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
                <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Memorial Website Setup</h1>
                <p class="lead mb-4">Welcome to your memorial website. To get started, you need to add obituary data to your MongoDB database.</p>
                
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body text-start">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Quick Setup Instructions:</h5>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Connect to your MongoDB database</li>
                            <li>Use the following sample data to create your first obituary:</li>
                        </ol>
                        
                        <pre class="bg-light p-3 rounded"><code>{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "1950-01-15",
  "dateOfPassing": "2024-01-01",
  "biography": "A loving father, grandfather, and friend to many...",
  "survivedBy": ["Jane Doe (Wife)", "Michael Doe (Son)", "Sarah Smith (Daughter)"],
  "tribute": "John lived a life full of love, laughter, and kindness...",
  "funeral": {
    "venue": "St. Mary's Church",
    "address": "123 Main Street, City, State",
    "date": "2024-01-05",
    "time": "10:00 AM",
    "googleMapsUrl": "https://maps.google.com/...",
    "liveStreamUrl": "https://youtube.com/..."
  },
  "photos": [],
  "language": "english",
  "isActive": true
}</code></pre>
                        
                        <p class="mt-3">Insert this into the 'obituaries' collection in your MongoDB database, then refresh this page.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
